name: Parrley's Battle Suits
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi - commissions open!
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

UPDATE: v1.0 - Dynamic Movement

A kind user pointed out that the original model was overfit on the neutral position. Therefore I retrained it and brought to you a more flexible model that will be able to depict action scenes!

Parrley's Battle Suits

Hello everyone,

I made this model to celebrate the fact that I've made a new friend today. A good lad that's soon going to be training his own LoRAs.

Let's encourage him through using and reviewing this model!

Let's go Parrley,
